{"tid":2439689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒：哈利梅根大爆王室秘辛惹怒女王　公爵夫婦頭銜恐不保","createTime":"2021-03-09T12:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T22:13:07.000Z","uid":223741,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2d1aeaa1140fabee430e141458d6b3a28931b2","tid":2439689,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"英國哈利王子和妻子梅根在美接受專訪，大爆夫婦倆與英國王室間的不睦與家醜。英國媒體披露，女王伊麗莎白二世對兩人爆料甚是惱怒，他們的公爵夫婦頭銜恐被摘除。<br />\n<br />\n頭銜為薩塞克斯公爵和公爵夫人（Duke and Duchess of Sussex）的哈利與梅根（Meghan Markle）接受美國電視脫口秀主持人歐普拉（Oprah Winfrey）專訪，梅根透露曾有輕生念頭卻求助無門，且懷兒子期間，王室內部有人議論寶寶皮膚會有多黑等等，這番談話重創英國王室形象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210309/4TKVB5BV45BJ5NDXETWQ7PUY4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2F4TKVB5BV45BJ5NDXETWQ7PUY4U%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=5a44f262\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2F4TKVB5BV45BJ5NDXETWQ7PUY4U%2F&h=1623d970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210309/4TKVB5BV45BJ5NDXETWQ7PUY4U/</a>"},{"pid":"b0577fce9a67e67cdd1653302511c4af9fec07c1","tid":2439689,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"同CCTVB D消息人士一樣9吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d57e669cd3a143006e5e2467f45d720489b99b5","tid":2439689,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"英國王子、薩塞克斯公爵哈利與妻子梅根近日接受美國知名脫口秀主持人歐普拉（Oprah Winfrey）專訪，昨（8）日在美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）播出，梅根在訪談過程中大爆英國王室種族歧視，與凱特爭執的各種內幕，引起外界熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n昨日也是國際婦女節，梅根的好友哈里曼（Misan Harriman）在社群平台貼出哈利、梅根與長子亞契（Archie）一家和樂的照片；而凱特王妃、卡蜜拉則是狗仔拍到，在梅根專訪播出後一臉面如死灰的模樣。<br />\n<br />\n英國攝影師哈里曼來自奈及利亞，是反種族歧視「黑命貴」（Black Lives Matter）的支持者，同時也是哈利、梅根兩人的好友。在CBS播出哈利夫妻的專訪後，哈里曼在Instagram、Twitter上公開一張未曾公開過的家庭照。<br />\n<br />\n照片中，哈利與梅根都沒有穿鞋子、光著腳，兩人穿著休閒，梅根的手裡抱著強褓中的亞契。哈里曼標注「國際婦女節」、「ipad攝影」等標籤外，還標注了「是個女孩」呼應梅根在訪問中透露第二胎的性別。<br />\n<br />\n凱特和卡蜜拉則是在倫敦被拍到，在節目播出後面色鐵青，特別是梅根指控凱特在婚禮前逼哭自己。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E5%87%B1%E7%89%B9%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%8D%E5%88%B0-%E8%87%89%E4%B8%8D%E7%88%BD-025913190.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAGMZzBYSuHuFeKH7FF6SXlb9P_X-3BFeZY-FjCzdR8a4Nfxl8op5ehk48hRuGrZsTL-rAPoRYLP4ycCIGY_1O6YXIBbWh2ulKjfKzUt_JnnQxvBaxVhobhHaCkaNu_WnMspQBnI8Tx7jILbPIAt3Vo70afj5j5gBglQ4ZBMQiUxI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2596%2599-%25E5%2587%25B1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E8%2587%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2588%25BD-025913190.html%3Fguccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAAGMZzBYSuHuFeKH7FF6SXlb9P_X-3BFeZY-FjCzdR8a4Nfxl8op5ehk48hRuGrZsTL-rAPoRYLP4ycCIGY_1O6YXIBbWh2ulKjfKzUt_JnnQxvBaxVhobhHaCkaNu_WnMspQBnI8Tx7jILbPIAt3Vo70afj5j5gBglQ4ZBMQiUxI&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=dc5a73c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E5%87%B1%E7%89%B9%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%8D%E5%88%B0-%E8%87%89%E4%B8%8D%E7%88%BD-025913190.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAGMZzBYSuHuFeKH7FF6SXlb9P_X-3BFeZY-FjCzdR8a4Nfxl8op5ehk48hRuGrZsTL-rAPoRYLP4ycCIGY_1O6YXIBbWh2ulKjfKzUt_JnnQxvBaxVhobhHaCkaNu_WnMspQBnI8Tx7jILbPIAt3Vo70afj5j5gBglQ4ZBMQiUxI</a>"},{"pid":"53ed257b5021f1289d422ab7cbca165aae7fc5ad","tid":2439689,"uid":89184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"「王室內部有人議論寶寶皮膚會有多黑等等」<br />\n<br />\n可能只係掃地嗰個阿嬸同同事吹水講過一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26bc765bbd01ad5644b55c6e6ac87545f736c